title: Heal Me
description:
Salmonella Dub have returned with their new recording, Heal Me, four years on from the multi platinum selling album, One Drop East.

Heal Me is an eleven track, vocally lush, musically seamless, horn laden, long player; featuring the bands hallmark
heavy rhythm section layered with Salmonella Dub psychedelic colourings.

TRACKLISTING:
01 Watching It Rain
02 Beat The Game
03 Love Sunshine And Happiness
04 Lightning
05 Heal Me
06 Rong
07 Gifts
08 That Easy
09 Seeds
10 Nothing Is Free
11 Hapuka Rain Outro

100% New Zealand Music
